@node DISKBASEDGAMES "Disk-based games"
@{jcenter}@{fg highlight}Disk-based games@{fg text}
@{jleft}
These are games that come in disk-loadable form these days, but were
originally sold as either tape-based games or cartridges. Many games of this
type fit on one disk, and a BASIC or DOS command is needed to load them.

