@node MEGAROMS "MegaROMs"
@{jcenter}@{fg highlight}MegaROMs@{fg text}
@{jleft}
MegaROMs are cartridges that are larger than 32K. Normally the MSX can only
use cartridges of 32K or smaller, but thanks to special circuitry inside the
cartridge it has become possible to use larger cartridge sizes.

Unfortunately this special hardware is different from cartridge to cartridge.
So far 6 types are being emulated by fMSX. The following tables list the name
of each game, and the cartridge type that is required to make the game work.
Be sure to select the listed soundmode for optimal listening pleasure!

    @{fg shine}MSX1 megaROMs@{fg text}

